# Open This Power BI Project

Open this file in Power BI Desktop:

`RetailEnterpriseAnalytics.pbip`

If Desktop asks to apply pending changes or refresh data, choose **Apply changes** / **Refresh**.

Power BI's local file connector requires an absolute root path. The model uses this project root, then appends the relative `Dataset` folder and CSV filename in each query:

`C:\Users\ironside\Downloads\New folder (2)\Retail-Enterprise-Analytics`

The report contains five named dashboard pages as placeholders. The data model, relationships, and measures are already defined so you can immediately build visuals.
